* JIRA Username: $ircconfigdoc.getValue("jiraUsername")
* JIRA Pattern: $ircconfigdoc.getValue("jiraPattern")
{{/velocity}}

To modify the configuration, go to the [[IRC Configuration page>>IRC.IRCConfig]].

